Title: "Always up" hosts are never stale
Level: 1
Component: core
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0b4
Date: 1488806295

When a host check command "Always assume host to be up" was configured, the
corresponding host went stale after some time.  This has been fixed, such
hosts are never stale.
